Activity: A23 - Enhance the cybersecurity at your home

Objective
The goal of this activity was to improve the cybersecurity of my home environment by identifying and strengthening a specific weak point.

Method
I reviewed my home network security and identified that the WiFi password could be improved. I updated the password to a stronger one using a combination of uppercase and lowercase letters, numbers, and special characters.

Findings
The following improvement was made:
1. Strengthened the WiFi password to reduce the risk of unauthorised access to the home network.

Security Principle
This activity supports confidentiality, as a strong WiFi password prevents unauthorised users from accessing the network and potentially intercepting sensitive data.

Evidence
- photos in evidence folder

Reflection
This activity showed that even a single small change can improve overall security. A weak WiFi password can expose the entire network, so strengthening it is an important and simple security measure.
